---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import Link from "@/components/ui/link.astro";
---

<section id="offerings" class="py-16">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 via-purple-500 to-indigo-500 dark:from-pink-400 dark:via-purple-300 dark:to-indigo-400">Our Workshop Offerings</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-lg text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto enhanced-text">We bring our expert trainers directly to your location for hands-on, immersive learning experiences</p>
  </div>

  <div class="knowledge-sharing-panel">
    <h3 class="knowledge-sharing-title">Share Your Knowledge</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-100 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed">
      We strongly encourage participants to share workshop materials and teach others what you've learned.
      This collaborative approach reinforces your own understanding and extends the benefits to your wider team.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-200 mt-3">
      <span class="font-semibold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300">Pro tip:</span> The first few days' content is especially valuable for sharing with colleagues!
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-3 italic">
      (Just keep those SSH keys and sensitive credentials to yourself â€” we trust you know that already.)
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="workshop-card p-8 rounded-xl transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
      <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-700 to-indigo-700 dark:from-purple-200 dark:to-indigo-200 mb-2 workshop-title">3-Day Rapid VibeCode Workshop</h3>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 via-purple-600 to-indigo-600 dark:from-pink-400 dark:via-purple-400 dark:to-indigo-300 text-transparent bg-clip-text my-4 drop-shadow-sm price-tag">$3,000 per seat</div>
        <p class="text-slate-900 font-medium dark:text-white mb-4 enhanced-text">Learn how to use Windsurf to accelerate your development process:</p>
        <ul class="text-slate-900 font-medium dark:text-white mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start workshop-list-item">
            <Icon name="bx:bxs-check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2" />
            <span><strong class="day-marker">Day 1:</strong> The Essence of Vibe Coding</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start workshop-list-item">
            <Icon name="bx:bxs-check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2" />
            <span><strong class="day-marker">Day 2:</strong> CLI-ing Everything</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start workshop-list-item">
            <Icon name="bx:bxs-check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2" />
            <span><strong class="day-marker">Day 3:</strong> Client Technology Integration</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-4">
          <Link href="/product-a" style="outline">Learn More</Link>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="workshop-card p-8 rounded-xl transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
      <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-700 to-indigo-700 dark:from-purple-200 dark:to-indigo-200 mb-2 workshop-title">5-Day Rapid VibeCode Workshop</h3>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 via-purple-600 to-indigo-600 dark:from-pink-400 dark:via-purple-400 dark:to-indigo-300 text-transparent bg-clip-text my-4 drop-shadow-sm price-tag">$4,500 per seat</div>
        <p class="text-slate-900 font-medium dark:text-white mb-4 enhanced-text">Everything in the 3-Day Workshop, plus two additional days:</p>
        <ul class="text-slate-900 font-medium dark:text-white mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start workshop-list-item">
            <Icon name="bx:bxs-check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2" />
            <span><strong class="day-marker">Day 4:</strong> Automating Business Development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start workshop-list-item">
            <Icon name="bx:bxs-check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-2" />
            <span><strong class="day-marker">Day 5:</strong> Idea Implementation & Prototyping</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-4">
          <Link href="/product-b" style="outline">Learn More</Link>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
